author: chayanit
body:
Update GENSIM string in 11_3_X according to #33010 for PPS workflows, and add back PPS workflows to IB test (removed in #33020). 

In addition, I think we should also update all Run3 workflows to 14TeV instead of 13TeV. This is for TTbar design Run3 2021 (12024 to 12034)

All GENSIM have been produced in 11_3_0_pre4
